This paper deals with natural language processing and summarization, which are typically covered under the arXiv category of Computation and Language (cs.CL). The use of Abstract Meaning Representation (AMR) also suggests a focus on semantic representation and understanding, which could fall under the sub-categories of Information Retrieval (cs.IR), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), and Machine Learning (cs.LG, cs.NE).
